decisions.details:
In workspace Cargo.toml:
[workspace.lints.clippy]
all = { level = "warn", priority = -1 }
pedantic = { level = "warn", priority = -1 }
nursery = { level = "warn", priority = -1 }
cargo = { level = "warn", priority = -1 }

Common pedantic allows: cast_precision_loss, module_name_repetitions, must_use_candidate, missing_errors_doc, missing_panics_doc.

Cherry-pick from restriction: dbg_macro, undocumented_unsafe_blocks, clone_on_ref_ptr, unwrap_used.

Member crates inherit with [lints] workspace = true.

CI runs: cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets --all-features with RUSTFLAGS="-Dwarnings".
